video_game_sales_clean %>% 
  group_by(platform) %>% 
  summarise(mean_sales = mean(global_sales)) %>% 
  ggplot() +
  aes(x = platform, y = mean_sales) +
  geom_col()

video_game_sales_clean %>% 
  filter(developer != "Nintendo") %>% 
  group_by(platform) %>% 
  summarise(mean_sales = mean(global_sales)) %>% 
  ggplot() +
  aes(x = platform, y = mean_sales) +
  geom_col()
